rows.label: qst002903_msg0001
rows.name:
That Linka Honey... wait before
you give it to Shibushibu, mo!

rows.label: qst002903_msg0002
rows.name:
Tsubutsubu is Shibushibu's
little sister, mo.

rows.label: qst002903_msg0003
rows.name: She has a weakness for sweets, mo.

rows.label: qst002903_msg0004
rows.name:
So, I'd like to see that Linka
Honey for a moment, mo.

rows.label: qst002903_msg0005
rows.name:
This color, this aroma...
it's wonderful, mo!

rows.label: qst002903_msg0006
rows.name:
I want you to bring
me more of this, mo.

rows.label: qst002903_msg0007
rows.name:
Only the Linka Honey will be
bought by Tsubutsubu, mo.

rows.label: qst002903_msg0008
rows.name:
I'll make sure to increase
your reward, mo.
